Package sep.gaia.resources.wikipedia

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    WikiMarkupParser
    Static class which holds the functionality to identify the short description and to convert it from the whole wikipedia article in wikipedia markup language.
    WikipediaCache
    WikipediaData objects are only stored in memory.
    WikipediaData
    Concrete class WikipediaData inherits from DataResource.
    WikipediaLoaderWorker
    The WikipediaLoaderWorker class object which runs in its own thread.
    WikipediaManager
    Management object to load wikipedia short descriptions from wikipedia.
    WikipediaWorkerFactory
    This class generates WikipediaLoaderWorker objects.
